<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176440' id='t-176440'>What they don't realize is that,
while they're watching their shows,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='179680' id='t-179680'>actually, they are being watched.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='182000' id='t-182000'>They are being watched
